	"Excellent…
	Let me restore your POKéMON."
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_PreparedFor2ndOpponent {
	"The 2nd opponent is next.
	Are you prepared?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_PreparedFor3rdOpponent {
	"The 3rd opponent is next.
	Are you prepared?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_PreparedFor4thOpponent {
	"The 4th opponent is next.
	Are you prepared?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_PreparedFor5thOpponent {
	"The 5th opponent is next.
	Are you prepared?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_PreparedFor6thOpponent {
	"The 6th opponent is next.
	Are you prepared?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_PreparedFor7thOpponent {
	"The 7th opponent is next.
	Are you prepared?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SaveAndQuitGame {
	"Would you like to save and quit
	the game?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_WishToQuitChallenge {
	"Do you wish to quit your challenge?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SavingData {
	"Saving the data.
	Have patience…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_RecordLastMatch {
	"Do you wish to record your latest
	match on your FRONTIER PASS?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_ChallengingPalaceMaven {
	"And now…

	By winning consistently, you have
	earned the privilege of challenging
	our master, the PALACE MAVEN…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_ReadyForPalaceMaven {
	"I shall send for the PALACE MAVEN.
	Are you ready?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_AnnounceArrivalOfSpenser {
	"Let great fanfare announce the arrival
	of the PALACE MAVEN, SPENSER!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserFirstIntro {
	"SPENSER: My physical being is with
	POKéMON always!

	My heart beats as one with
	POKéMON always!

	Young one of a TRAINER!
	Do you believe in your POKéMON?

	Can you believe them through
	and through?

	If your bonds of trust are frail,
	you will never beat my brethren!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_ProveYourBondWithMons {
	"The bond you share with your POKéMON!
	Prove it to me here!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserPostSilverBattle {
	"SPENSER: Gwahahah!

	Hah, you never fell for my bluster!
	Sorry for trying that stunt!

	Here!
	Bring me the thing!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_LetsSeeFrontierPass {
	"My, my, if only you could maintain that
	facade of distinguished authority…

	Here!
	Let's see your FRONTIER PASS!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_ReceivedSpiritsSymbol {
	"The Spirits Symbol was embossed on
	the FRONTIER PASS!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserAwaitNextTime {
	"SPENSER: Your POKéMON's eyes are 
	truly clear and unclouded.

	I will eagerly await the next
	opportunity to see you."
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserThisTimeWontHoldBack {
	"SPENSER: Gwahahah!
	You've battled your way up again?

	You must have developed a truly
	formidable bond with your POKéMON.

	So be it!

	This time, I won't bluster or hold back.
	This time, there's no fooling around.

	Ready now?
	Prepare to lose!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_Kaaah {
	"… … …Kaaah!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserYourTeamIsAdmirable {
	"SPENSER: Well, that was some display!
	Even fully unleashed, my brethren
	could not overpower you.

	Your team spirit is truly admirable!

	Here!
	Bring me that thing, will you?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_HurryWithFrontierPass {
	"My, my, if only you could maintain
	a certain level of decorum…

	Gaaah, here!
	Hurry with that FRONTIER PASS, you!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpiritsSymbolTookGoldenShine {
	"The Spirits Symbol took on
	a golden shine!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserComeSeeMeAgain {
	"SPENSER: Gwahahah!

	Come see me time and again!
	My brethren and I will be waiting!"
}
